Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.97,0:00:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.37,0:00:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  只是失去意識而已
